{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/store-multiple-values-in-one-variable-using-javascript-arrays","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Sacuvajte Vise Vrednosti u Jednoj Promenljivoj Koristeci JavaScript Nizove","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Koristeci JavaScript <code>array</code> promenljive, mozemo cuvati vise delova podataka na jednom mestu.</p>\n<p>Deklaraciju niza zapocinjete otvorenom uglastom zagradom, zavrsavate zatvorenom uglastom zagradom i stavljate zarez izmedju svake stavke, ovako:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const sandwich = [\"peanut butter\", \"jelly\", \"bread\"];\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"bd7993c9c69feddfaeb8bdef","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Izmenite novi niz <code>myArray</code> tako da sadrzi string i broj (tim redosledom).</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18309,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/store-multiple-values-in-one-variable-using-javascript-arrays"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Only change code below this line\nconst myArray = [];","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>myArray</code> treba da bude niz.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof myArray == 'object');"},{"text":"<p>Prvi element u <code>myArray</code> treba da bude string.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof myArray[0] !== 'undefined' && typeof myArray[0] == 'string');"},{"text":"<p>Drugi element u <code>myArray</code> tr